001package edu.cnm.deepdive.spaceseek;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.navigation.ActionOnlyNavDirections;
005import androidx.navigation.NavDirections;
006
007public class NavGraphDirections {
008  private NavGraphDirections() {
009  }
010
011  @NonNull
012  public static NavDirections navigateToSettingsFragment() {
013    return new ActionOnlyNavDirections(R.id.navigate_to_settings_fragment);
014  }
015
016  @NonNull
017  public static NavDirections navigateToPreLoginFragment() {
018    return new ActionOnlyNavDirections(R.id.navigate_to_pre_login_fragment);
019  }
020
021  @NonNull
022  public static NavDirections navigateToImageFragment() {
023    return new ActionOnlyNavDirections(R.id.navigate_to_image_fragment);
024  }
025}
